text: The Jets are a Tongan American pop and R&B; family band from Robbinsdale, a suburb of Minneapolis, Minnesota. The Jets are composed of brothers and sisters LeRoy, Eddie, Eugene, Haini, Rudy, Kathi, Elizabeth, and Moana Wolfgramm, who perform pop, R&B;, and dance music. They started performing as a family band in 1977. The group enjoyed worldwide success in 1985â€“1990, performing three world tours, and producing five top-10 hits on the US Billboard Hot 100.
